content:
Hi Daniela,

I saw that Keith’s account sent over a recommendation—does that mean the repost idea is off the table? Totally understand if that wasn’t an option, but if there’s still room for it, I’d be happy to tweak the messaging however needed to make it work. That would be so huge! It's like at the tipping point of virality and have had a few thought leaders comment/reach out.

Either way, I really appreciate the team’s time and the recommendation—grateful for the support!

Thanks,
Jesse
